## ğŸ”— 4. Network Proximity Calculation

- **Graph:** Human_PPI (STRING v12.0) â€” ENSPâ€“ENSP edges  
- **Distance options:**
  - Precomputed full matrix (`DistMatrix`)  
  - Incremental memmap row caching (`rows_mm.npy`)

### ğŸ§  Output Format

```python
{
  "shortest": <observed mean distance>,
  "Z_score": {
      "d": <observed>,
      "z": <Z-score>,
      "mean": <random mean>,
      "std": <random std>,
      "p": <empirical p-value>
  }
}
